00:49:35,305 --> 00:49:36,306
SEASONAL FLAVOR

937
00:49:38,241 --> 00:49:39,443
Scissors, shoot!

938
00:49:40,577 --> 00:49:42,279
I did it!

939
00:49:42,346 --> 00:49:44,448
-Mom wins!
-Hey!

940
